<p>GitHub: <a href="https://github.com/cpavlina/bomtool">cpavlina/bomtool</a></p>

<p>bomtool is a KiCad/DigiKey BOM (Bill Of Materials) manager. It lets you specify
parts in a KiCad schematic like this:</p>

<pre>
RES SMD 20k 1% [0402]
CAP MLCC 33nF 5% 25V â‰¥X5R [0603]
BEAD SMD 100 @100MHz 2A [1206]
</pre>

<p>bomtool will then open a browser and drive DigiKey's parametric search to
find the parts for you. It does more &mdash; check out
<a href="http://cgi.c4757p.com/ghview.py?bomtool/master/DOCUMENTATION.html">the
documentation</a>!</p>

